{"type": "article", "id": 6991, "title": "亮橙色可能流行，至少对时装来说是这样", "description": "不同的设计、剪裁和材质，都赋予了橙色不同的效果。", "date": "2015-03-02T13:55:48Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 7392, "name": "橙色"}, {"id": 7393, "name": "流行色"}, {"id": 7397, "name": "MSGM"}], "category": 19, "author": 37534, "comment_count": 4, "praise_count": 34, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160604225608IM72Lv4olKgGn9qV.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t纵览今年的伦敦、纽约、米兰时装周，亮橙色大放异彩。<a href=\"http://www.style.com/fashion-shows/fall-2015-ready-to-wear/altuzarra\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"background-color:#FFFFFF;\">Altuzarra 的手包</a>、<a href=\"http://www.style.com/fashion-shows/fall-2015-ready-to-wear/bottega-veneta\" target=\"_blank\">Bottega Veneta</a> 的毛衣和围巾、<a href=\"http://www.style.com/fashion-shows/fall-2015-ready-to-wear/msgm\" target=\"_blank\">Jil Sander</a> 和<a href=\"http://msgm.it/\" target=\"_blank\"> MSGM</a> 的靴子……<a href=\"http://www.style.com/trends/accessories/2015/orange-boots-jil-sander-msgm\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"background-color:#FFFFFF;\">橙色真是无处不在</a>。Jil Sander 品牌的创意总监 Rodolfo Paglialunga 和 MSGM 的创始人 Massimo Giorgetti 的最新设计都践行了梵高的名言：如果没有橙色的映衬，蓝色也将不再存在（There is no blue…without orange）。不同的设计、剪裁和材质，都赋予了橙色不同的效果。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160604225602NSksKdAXT9rWRy74.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.5\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<em>MSGM 的新品</em> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160604225602dmoO4wQ8GlBFfhXJ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.5\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160604225603EqOYwFn4avAUckN7.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.5\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201606042256038VcMZyjmH3puGfsN.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.5\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">\r\n\t<span><em>MSGM </em><a href=\"http://www.style.com/fashion-shows/fall-2015-ready-to-wear\"><em>Fall 2015\r\nReady-to-Wear</em></a></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\tMSGM 是 2008 年由意大利设计师 Massimo\r\nGiorgetti 创立的，意欲以充满玩味的方式将传统款式重新演绎。他们的作品用色大多较为大胆，在剪裁上又忠诚于古典的意大利风格，两种特色交融搭配。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160604225604B5CwefPxZnAYU8OF.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.5\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">\r\n\t<span><a href=\"http://www.style.com/fashion-shows/fall-2015-ready-to-wear/altuzarra\">Altuzarra</a> </span>的模特 <span>Annika Krijt </span>演绎了橙色的手包\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160604225605eALZGP9uhtlbROo4.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.3171875\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">\r\n\t美国时尚博主 <span>Jane Aldridge </span>染一头金灿灿的橙黄发色，前卫感即显。<span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<img src=\"img/uploads/20160604225605Szti0spaIBEkMQNW.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.5\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n<p>\r\n\t戛纳影后 Charlotte Gainsbourg 一身 LV 橙色装扮。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160604225606TJLI840DGYrU39yN.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.5\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">\r\n\t丹麦时尚博主 <span>Pernille Teisbaek </span>的造型，整体搭配以橙黄为主灰色为辅，配色经典。<span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160604225606EYlVCsMX9pdeZhzB.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.665625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">\r\n\t<span>Charlotte Olympia </span>品牌创始人兼设计师 <span>Chaelotte Dellal </span>和时尚达人珠宝顾问 <span>Alix Duvernoy</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">\r\n\t<span><img src=\"img/uploads/20160604225607BQKiDNo213LJX9tS.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.5\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><br>\r\n</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">\r\n\t<span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">\r\n\t<span>New York Fashion Week: DKNY Spring/Summer\r\n2015</span>，<span>DKNY </span>这一季的主打颜色就是橙。<span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160604225607rT0PtOy6hA152NjX.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.5015625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<span style=\"white-space:normal;\">DIOR 15 Spring Summer collection</span>\n\n\n"}